    <item>
      <title>花旗集团称华尔街卖空者已认输</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/wall-street-short-sellers-throwing-in-the-towel-citigroup-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团策略师表示，由于标准普尔 500 指数不断创下历史新高并有望创下 2021 年以来的最佳表现，空头正在屈服，而对欧洲股市的持仓仍然看跌，这进一步扩大了两个市场之间的差距。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/wall-street-short-sellers-throwing-in-the-towel-citigroup-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 09:18:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>因 GDP 意外放缓，看跌卢比的期权押注上涨 200%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/bearish-options-bets-on-rupee-jump-200-on-surprise-gdp-slowdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示印度经济增长大幅放缓后，期权交易员增加了对印度卢比的看跌押注，这进一步给印度卢比带来压力，使其在最近几天创下一系列历史低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/bearish-options-bets-on-rupee-jump-200-on-surprise-gdp-slowdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 07:40:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
